🟢 Decision proposal:
v0 = 6–7 boss locations only



v0 Items
We only randomize hard progression:

Core items
* Vine Rune
* Teleport Rune
* Ram Rune
* Spider Rune

Meta progression
Boss Cell 1
Boss Cell 2
Boss Cell 3
Boss Cell 4
Boss Cell 5

That’s 9 items total.

Why these are ideal
Already binary or numeric flags
No inventory clutter
No balance chaos
Naturally understood by players



Basic logic

Early bosses require no runes
Mid bosses require some runes
Late bosses require all runes + BCs

